WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:08.561
Hey, good morning family. I just want to say thank you to all the people who came out for the Arise Conference with Sister Billie and Rick Renner.

00:00:08.562 --> 00:00:18.442
It was wonderful. We have one more day, which is Sunday, and we're having services tomorrow morning and tomorrow night at 7:00.

00:00:18.443 --> 00:00:32.008
We're excited about it; it’s the finale, and I'm believing God for a major move of His presence, a glorious outpouring of His Spirit on the last night, which is tomorrow night.

00:00:32.009 --> 00:00:38.308
It's been so exciting to see every single one of you. Thank you for driving so far to be a part of this conference.

00:00:38.309 --> 00:00:42.616
There were a lot of you who drove from all over the place, from Maine to Michigan.

00:00:42.617 --> 00:00:52.296
I talked to a man from Colorado who has been coming to all the meetings, so it's exciting to see your faces.

00:00:52.297 --> 00:01:18.482
It’s great to put a face with the name from an email and say, 'Oh, that's who you are.'It’s exciting because y’all are so kind; you email us and always try to encourage us, and you're so faithful.

00:01:18.483 --> 00:01:24.993
I think it's interesting, I have some things on my heart. Bill Gates went on *The View*.

00:01:24.995 --> 00:01:53.637
Some people sent this to me and said, 'Brandon, did you see what Bill Gates said on *The View* about the plague and all that?'I said, 'Go figure,'but he went on *The View* and told everybody that he thought there would be another plague happening within the next four years—a major one, worse than COVID—just like I told you all that they were planning something worse than COVID, like the Black Death.

00:01:53.638 --> 00:01:58.839
He went on to say all these dark things. Let me show you that little clip right here.

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:04.410
Before COVID, you said you spent the most sleepless nights worrying about pandemics.

00:02:04.411 --> 00:02:12.912
After COVID, has that changed? And if it has, what keeps you up now? Because we all need to know.

00:02:12.913 --> 00:02:20.613
Yeah, the pandemic, sadly, was fairly predictable, and it won't be the last pandemic.

00:02:20.614 --> 00:02:27.551
The next one could be far more severe. I mean, this one killed millions; it was awful.

00:02:27.552 --> 00:02:36.469
We got the vaccine. President Trump's leadership was a factor in getting that out quickly.

00:02:36.470 --> 00:02:53.239
When I spoke to him, I said, 'Here are some other medical innovations, including a thing called an HIV cure that could be accelerated.'So, we should be more prepared for a pandemic; I'd say that's still number one.

00:02:53.240 --> 00:03:05.172
You can worry about nuclear war, AI—oh, there’s plenty to worry about—but overall, I'm an optimist.

00:03:05.173 --> 00:03:11.067
It’s up to the government to think ahead on behalf of the citizens.

00:03:11.068 --> 00:03:20.039
Regarding a pandemic, there's a lot that we should be doing that hopefully we'll get our act together before the next one comes.

00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:27.732
Overall, innovation in health, both in developing countries and the rich world, I love being part of that.

00:03:27.733 --> 00:03:32.658
I was reading, though, that you said the next pandemic you are predicting within maybe 25 years.

00:03:32.659 --> 00:03:37.090
Is that certain? Certainly, we'll have one in the next 25 years.

00:03:37.091 --> 00:03:48.084
There are even some pathogens out there that we're watching right now. So, maybe a 10% chance in the next four years.

00:03:48.085 --> 00:03:59.023
Folks, they're telling you what they're planning; it's how they're going to try to derail Trump's presidency to try to not let him do all the things he’s wanting to do.

00:03:59.024 --> 00:04:09.115
I saw the darkness of them trying—the Antichrist agenda trying to stop and derail the things that God was trying to do.

00:04:09.116 --> 00:04:21.547
Now, I believe the plague has a great opportunity to take place; maybe we can delay it, maybe we can't, but I'm telling you all it's not for us to fear.

00:04:21.548 --> 00:04:41.567
The Lord said if you get Psalm 91 deep down inside of your heart and Psalm 23—I told you all I saw a major storm coming on the East Coast; a major storm was coming and it starts in Europe.

00:04:41.567 --> 00:04:59.999
The Lord showed me a great shaking to awaken is coming. Whenever I talked to Sister Billie, she said, 'Brandon, we want something greater than a revival,'and what's greater than a revival is an awakening unto God.

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:03.840
That's what the Lord told me: 'Brandon, I'm going to bring an awakening to the church.

00:05:03.841 --> 00:05:21.795
There's a great shaking to awaken.'So, I want you all to be encouraged that this isn't about fear for you Bible-believing, Holy Ghost-filled, on-fire-for-Jesus people.

00:05:21.796 --> 00:05:28.661
This is a time to arise and shine for the light has come and the glory of the Lord is risen upon you.

00:05:28.662 --> 00:05:35.774
This is not going to be a time for you to go, 'Oh no, Chicken Little, the sky is falling.'I do not believe that.

00:05:35.774 --> 00:05:44.928
I believe it's time for the glorious church to rise up and take their authority like we've never seen before.

00:05:44.929 --> 00:05:53.103
The Bible says that He's coming for a bride without spot or wrinkle, and we will be that glorious church.

00:05:53.104 --> 00:06:06.157
What is it going to take to get there? I was standing there getting my daughter ready for church tonight and the Lord spoke to me.

00:06:06.158 --> 00:06:13.314
I was frustrated because I was brushing her hair and helping Diana get ready because we were running late, and the Lord spoke to me.

00:06:13.315 --> 00:06:29.719
He said, 'Brandon, when are you going to shift your thinking for Megan to believe for her now?'She's healed instead of always—because He heard my heart—complaining about what I was doing.

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:35.078
He said to me, 'When are you going to believe Me that today is the day?

00:06:35.079 --> 00:06:45.166
Why is it that your heart is always, "Well, it'll come one day; her manifestation is going to come one day"?'I believe it.

00:06:45.167 --> 00:06:51.947
He said, 'When are you going to shift it to now-faith as the substance of things hoped for and evidence of things not seen?

00:06:51.948 --> 00:07:04.315
When are you going to believe for her now, Brandon? Why not?'And then He said this to me: 'Why not tonight?

00:07:04.316 --> 00:07:11.260
Why not tonight? And if not tonight, why not tomorrow night?

00:07:11.261 --> 00:07:17.649
Why do you put off in your mind that this may happen in a couple of years?'That's what He was correcting me on.

00:07:17.650 --> 00:07:21.594
I stopped and said, 'Lord...'He said, 'When are you believing for it?

00:07:21.595 --> 00:07:27.169
When do you really believe for it? Why are you believing for years from now?

00:07:27.170 --> 00:07:54.219
Believe Me for the now.'So I want to encourage you all: there's a lot of things you've been believing for, like finances, and it may not seem like you're ever going to get out of poverty, get a good job, or that your marriage is ever going to turn around, but suddenly things change.

00:07:54.220 --> 00:08:10.927
Joseph was in prison for 14 years, but he didn't know all his circumstances were going to change in a 24-hour period and he was going to be second-in-command of all Egypt.

00:08:10.928 --> 00:08:19.342
There was a 'suddenly.'There is a time where all the trials and the things you've been going through will have an expiration date.

00:08:19.343 --> 00:08:30.022
When is your expiration date? The Lord said for your life and what you're believing for, when is that time of that miracle coming for you?

00:08:30.023 --> 00:08:41.911
If we're always believing for later—which I have been—like, 'One day, Lord, in the sweet by-and-by Megan's going to get over that.'Why not now?

00:08:41.912 --> 00:08:50.898
Mark 11:24: 'Whatsoever things you desire, when you pray, believe that you receive them, and you shall have them.'Do you understand?

00:08:50.899 --> 00:09:00.479
'Whatever things you desire, when you pray, believe that you receive them, and you'll have them.'That's the first part of the verse.

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:16.639
I said, 'Forgive me, Lord,'because we always try to be so spiritual; we try to act like we're faking it, saying 'I'm believing,'but are you truly believing?

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:24.637
Are you really believing? That's what He was showing me: 'Do you really believe this?'I'm going to question you: do you really believe your unsaved loved ones are coming?

00:09:24.638 --> 00:09:33.747
How would we act if today they called you and said, 'Mom, Dad, Grandma, Grandpa, I got born again today'?

00:09:33.748 --> 00:09:42.288
Instead of 'one day they'll get saved, I'm believing before they die they'll get saved,'what if we start believing in the now?

00:09:42.289 --> 00:09:54.961
The Lord said, 'Start believing for the now.'All we see about the great shaking—I'll go back to that—I know what the Lord has shown me: there's a great shaking to awaken.

00:09:54.962 --> 00:10:07.759
I know there are major things about to take place. It's all about the people that are coming and running with the—we're ready with the catcher's mitts, ready to get the people that are coming.

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:16.694
The shaking to awaken is for the great revival, for us to have this major outpouring of the Spirit like we had at these services.

00:10:16.695 --> 00:10:24.124
We're waiting and anticipating the manifestations of the glory, saying, 'God, let's do it tonight.

00:10:24.125 --> 00:10:30.906
God, let's see somebody get healed tonight.'Where is the glorious outpouring?

00:10:30.907 --> 00:10:35.844
Where's it at, Lord? I'm believing it's going to happen tonight.

00:10:35.845 --> 00:10:40.719
I'm believing my unsaved loved one's going to get born again today.

00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:54.779
Always have an expectation for the manifestation of what you're believing for, never losing sight of being fully persuaded that what God has promised, He's able also to perform.

00:10:54.780 --> 00:11:02.159
I believe I receive what the Lord has told me He would do, and I'm not going to get weary in well-doing.

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:15.953
I'm going to keep my eyes focused on Him, seeking Him, staying vertical regardless of what the finances say, regardless of what my checkbook says, or what my bank statement says.

00:11:15.954 --> 00:11:27.136
I am not moved by what I see; I'm not moved by what I feel; I'm moved by what the word of God says. That's what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:11:27.137 --> 00:11:41.360
Many of you are going from paycheck to paycheck; you're barely making it and you know that everything you've earned today was spent three days ago.

00:11:41.361 --> 00:11:45.993
You're thinking, 'How in the world am I ever going to get out of this circumstance?

00:11:45.994 --> 00:11:55.573
How am I ever going to get out of this hole that I've been in?'We're so in debt that the debt is over us and the bill collectors are calling every single day.

00:11:55.574 --> 00:12:07.310
But there is a 'suddenly.'The Lord told me to tell you this today because I said, 'Lord, how do I present this?'He said, 'Tell them what you're going through right now.

00:12:07.311 --> 00:12:16.109
We're all a work in progress.'We're all believing for something today. If you're not, you should be.

00:12:16.110 --> 00:12:30.885
Believe God to do something big in your life because He's able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think, according to the power that worketh through you and in you.

00:12:30.886 --> 00:12:39.748
We are His children; the spirit of man is the candle of the Lord.

00:12:39.749 --> 00:12:47.042
I believe with all my heart it's time to believe God for the impossible.

00:12:47.043 --> 00:13:01.094
You may think, 'I'm never going to get out of this financial hole,'or 'I'm always going to be at the bottom of the barrel and the barrel is on top of me,'but it's time to change that stinking thinking.

00:13:01.095 --> 00:13:23.822
It's time to think, 'My husband or my wife is going to come to Jesus.'They're going to have that supernatural visitation from the Lord in their sleep; they're going to have that supernatural Holy Ghost experience on the way home from work today. When I get home today, my wife's going to be there.

00:13:23.823 --> 00:13:48.233
You say, if your wife's a stay-at-home mom, 'She's going to have something that's going to tug at her and she'll say, "Honey, I had an experience with Jesus today."'You say, 'I've never had that before; my wife is not saved and doesn't want anything to do with Jesus.'But there's always that 'suddenly'; there's an expiration date for what you're going through.

00:13:48.234 --> 00:13:55.799
I believe with all my heart, I hear that in my spirit today to tell you: there's an expiration date for what you're going through.

00:13:55.800 --> 00:14:13.168
The Lord told me to tell you it's time to believe God for big. It's time to believe Him for big in your life today, that there will be sudden things, a sudden change. I got hope when I saw tonight.

00:14:13.169 --> 00:14:37.429
Megan had a rough night at church, but I said I'm not moved, even when she was squirming around on the back row and we had to take her out because I thought, 'Man, this is embarrassing.'The guest speaker was sitting behind us as he got there late, and I thought, 'This is a very embarrassing moment because of how Megan is acting,'but I said I'm not moved by what I see.

00:14:37.430 --> 00:14:52.155
I said, 'God, I'm believing for the now.'But see, the devil always comes to challenge your 'now'to try to knock you down right before you know that your breakthrough is right there at the door.

00:14:52.156 --> 00:15:09.120
Tomorrow is the Super Bowl, and there are a lot of times you'll see them go all the way to the end zone, and right at the one-yard line—fourth and goal for those who like football—it's when it's the hardest to make the touchdown.

00:15:09.121 --> 00:15:19.059
A lot of times you just got to get a couple of inches, but it seems to be the hardest.

00:15:19.060 --> 00:15:37.094
If you don't give up, if you keep on keeping on and keep looking—even when the devil comes immediately like he did tonight to try to knock me down and say, 'You had that word in the house, ha ha ha, Megan acted up'—I got frustrated and tired of it.

00:15:37.095 --> 00:15:44.938
I looked at her and thought, 'Wow, this is a rough night tonight.'My wife said, 'What was that all about?

00:15:44.939 --> 00:15:51.153
That was a hard night.'I said it's because he immediately comes to challenge the word of what the Lord said.

00:15:51.154 --> 00:15:59.799
He comes to try to kick you and knock you down, but if you stand up and say, 'I'm standing up on the inside, sucker.

00:15:59.800 --> 00:16:21.093
I don't care how you try to kick me in the gut and knock me down; I'm standing on the inside, and there's an expiration date to my circumstances.'I am not moved by what I see; I'm not moved by what I feel; I'm moved by what the Word says.

00:16:21.094 --> 00:16:33.655
I'm telling you tonight folks, I'm living it. You say, 'Well, Brother, you have it all together.'No, I'm living it.

00:16:33.656 --> 00:16:44.890
I'm an example of somebody who's standing by faith for something they've not seen in 20 years, but the Lord said there's an expiration date.

00:16:44.891 --> 00:16:49.452
What's your expiration date? What are you believing Him for?

00:16:49.453 --> 00:17:00.296
What are you saying in your heart, 'I'm not moved by what I see; I'm not moved by what I feel; I'm moved by what the word of God says'?

00:17:00.297 --> 00:17:18.824
He said all things are possible to him who believes. Do you believe that?

00:17:18.825 --> 00:17:33.460
I want to say with everything I have: all things are possible to him who believes. Your unsaved loved one is coming home today.

00:17:33.461 --> 00:17:37.884
Your wife's going to have a turnaround today; your husband's going to have a turnaround today.

00:17:37.885 --> 00:17:43.519
Your marriage is coming out of the hole; your marriage is going to get rekindled. You're going to fall in love with each other.

00:17:43.520 --> 00:17:58.008
In this time of love, we will not get out of love; we choose to walk in love with our unsaved loved ones no matter what we see, no matter how ugly they act.

00:17:58.009 --> 00:18:18.373
They may come in and cuss you out or do something crazy, and you go, 'Lord, I thought you told me they're coming home.'No, I'm not moved by what I see.

00:18:18.374 --> 00:18:22.373
I'm calling those things that be not as though they were today.

00:18:22.374 --> 00:18:38.308
My husband is saved, my wife is saved, my children are saved; they are healed, they are whole, they are well.

00:18:38.309 --> 00:18:43.558
Father, I thank You, Lord, that You sent Your angels to war on my behalf.

00:18:43.559 --> 00:18:51.904
Holy Spirit, I need Your help; I'm in a ditch, come and get me out.

00:18:51.905 --> 00:18:59.558
The Holy Spirit's an ever-present help in a time of need, and He pulls you out of that ditch.

00:18:59.559 --> 00:19:33.474
But it's our stinking thinking that derails us and we get down in that pity party, saying, 'Woe is me, feel sorry for me.'No, it's not always easy when you're going through it, but it's what's standing on the inside.

00:19:33.475 --> 00:20:07.729
I am not moved by what I see. I know there's a lot of you hurting inside and you may have had the worst week ever, saying 'I am so tired of being depressed or having anxiety or a fighting marriage.'But there's an expiration date.

00:20:07.730 --> 00:20:17.088
I choose to believe the expiration date is today. I want you to believe today with me.

00:20:17.089 --> 00:20:27.355
It says where two or more agree in touching anything, I'll be your two.

00:20:27.356 --> 00:20:41.195
I'll agree with you today for your unsaved loved ones and that you have expiration dates right there.

00:20:41.196 --> 00:20:48.856
Joseph had his season of great change. He surely thought, 'Am I going to be in this prison?

00:20:48.857 --> 00:21:10.454
All I did was try to honor God by not sleeping with Potiphar's wife, and she said I raped her when I didn't touch her.'He could have been up there whining, but he feared God and chose not to murmur and complain.

00:21:10.455 --> 00:21:25.558
He could have cursed God and died, but he chose to fear the Lord and interpreted a dream for Pharaoh, and lo and behold, he got out of that pit and became second-in-command.

00:21:25.559 --> 00:21:41.268
Your circumstances can change just like his did. God is no respecter of persons, and what He did for Joseph thousands of years ago, He'll do for you today.

00:21:41.269 --> 00:21:54.788
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever. Yet we see all these things about plagues and earthquakes in the news; we know we're in the signs of the times.

00:21:54.789 --> 00:22:13.333
I warned you about this and that, but right now the Lord is telling me to tell you He wants you to believe Him for big.

00:22:13.334 --> 00:22:19.954
Major alarm bells are going off in the spirit realm, but the Lord's coming back for a glorious church.

00:22:19.955 --> 00:22:25.588
It's time for the body of Christ to arise and shine for the light has come.

00:22:25.589 --> 00:22:52.970
We are going to be the salt and the light, and people are going to run to us and say, 'What is it that's different about you?'I've said this many times: it will be like a quarter; you'll have the dark on one side and light on the other.

00:22:52.971 --> 00:23:08.630
What do you choose to focus on? The Lord said great sobering days are coming.

00:23:08.631 --> 00:23:22.358
You can focus on the glorious church or you can focus on the darkness, the plagues, pestilence, wars, signs in the heavens, and asteroids.

00:23:22.359 --> 00:23:30.033
It's going to freak everybody out, but are you the one who is stable, saying 'I'm a King's kid.

00:23:30.034 --> 00:23:37.561
He's got me. I'm protected. I'm always in the right place at the right time. I'm never where a terrorist attack is going to be.

00:23:37.562 --> 00:24:03.496
I am where God wants me.'Be filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit today.

00:24:03.497 --> 00:24:12.950
How hungry and desperate are you for change in your life today?

00:24:12.951 --> 00:24:25.332
I choose to believe with you for your healing. So let's take communion right now together. I just wanted to tell you there's an expiration date.

00:24:25.333 --> 00:24:41.897
There are levels of glory; He's talking to me about what it takes to get to the glory and He gave me Romans.

00:24:41.898 --> 00:24:49.723
I really want you to memorize the whole passage of Romans chapter 8.

00:24:49.724 --> 00:25:02.973
Verse 18 talks about the suffering whenever you go through the Refiner's Fire; it causes the glory to come on you.

00:25:02.974 --> 00:25:09.079
The greater the affliction, the greater the glory on your life.

00:25:09.080 --> 00:25:21.966
Glory and challenge go hand in hand. Refiner's fire and glory go hand in hand according to Romans.

00:25:21.967 --> 00:25:33.821
I choose not to let these circumstances define me. This is not who I am; this is just a place I'm moving through.

00:25:33.822 --> 00:25:41.060
Yea, though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death, I will fear no evil.

00:25:41.061 --> 00:25:54.567
Sometimes you have to walk through the valley, but you have to keep walking. Thy rod and thy staff, they comfort me.

00:25:54.568 --> 00:26:20.345
He will deliver you from the snare of the fowler, but sometimes you still have to walk through the valley.

00:26:20.346 --> 00:26:26.724
Many are the afflictions of the righteous, but the Lord said He would deliver us out of them all.

00:26:26.725 --> 00:27:04.239
When you get through that valley, it's the Refiner's Fire that causes us to go up higher.

00:27:04.240 --> 00:27:09.965
We're going to see a major outpouring of the Spirit of the Lord beyond anything we've ever seen before.

00:27:09.966 --> 00:27:19.435
Father, we just thank You for all You've done for us. We thank You for Your body that was broken for us.

00:27:19.436 --> 00:27:29.776
You were wounded for our transgressions and bruised for our iniquities; the chastisement of our peace was upon You and with Your stripes we are healed.

00:27:29.777 --> 00:27:44.216
Lord, we thank You that You suffered and died. According to Galatians, Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

00:27:44.217 --> 00:28:16.543
I thank You for the 'now,'for the expiration date of it. We call healing over our bodies and we say today is our victory and deliverance.

00:28:16.544 --> 00:28:35.365
Rick Renner said, 'If you start asking the Holy Spirit for help, it’s like an old tea kettle.'It takes a little bit sometimes for the water to make that boiling sound, but if you keep on seeking Him and praying in the spirit, eventually that kettle’s going to start to whistle.

00:28:35.366 --> 00:29:04.043
So be steady and keep on keeping on. Lord, we take this body right now in the name of Jesus.

00:29:04.044 --> 00:29:18.030
Thank You, Father, that we don't have to go through this anymore.

00:29:18.031 --> 00:29:24.967
We plead the blood over our unsaved loved ones and thank You that they're saved and healed.

00:29:24.968 --> 00:30:42.535
We thank You for jobs and better jobs. We apply the blood around our house; no weapon formed against us will prosper.

00:30:42.536 --> 00:30:49.571
God has not given us a spirit of fear, but of power, and of love, and of a well-balanced mind.

00:30:49.572 --> 00:31:08.654
Now, Father, the Bible says that Satan has blinded the eyes of the unbeliever, and we take authority over those eyes right now that they would be flooded with light.

00:31:08.655 --> 00:31:31.170
I say in the name of Jesus that they have that 'suddenly'experience with the Holy Spirit right now, that they will no longer be on this path to hell but will be radically born again and ready for the coming of the Lord.

00:31:31.171 --> 00:31:37.125
I thank You that those unsaved loved ones are coming to Jesus right now as we speak.

00:31:37.126 --> 00:32:23.555
If you need Jesus, let me lead you in the sinner's prayer. Say this with me: 'Jesus, I believe You're the Son of God.

00:32:23.556 --> 00:32:42.987
I believe that You died and rose again on the third day. Jesus, I'm a sinner and I need a savior.

00:32:42.988 --> 00:32:51.353
Forgive me, Lord, and write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

00:32:51.354 --> 00:33:11.624
I want to make You my Lord and personal savior. Thank You, Lord, for forgiving me of my sins.

00:33:11.625 --> 00:33:22.281
I love You, Lord, and I'll serve You all the days of my life.'That's all you have to do.

00:33:22.282 --> 00:33:27.844
Tell somebody in the comment section if you just gave your heart to Jesus.

00:33:27.845 --> 00:34:18.350
We want to rejoice with you. If you don't have a Bible, email us and we'll send you one for free.

00:34:18.351 --> 00:34:25.025
Find a Bible-believing church, get baptized, and keep fanning your flame for Jesus.

00:34:25.026 --> 00:35:44.068
Don't let it go cold. Now, let's pray for your healing. Reach forth and grab a hold of His garment by faith.

00:35:44.069 --> 00:36:39.381
The woman with the issue of blood said, 'If I could touch the hem of His garment, I'll be made whole.'He said, 'Daughter, your faith has made you whole.'If her faith made her whole, your faith will make you whole.

00:36:39.382 --> 00:37:00.542
Life and death are in the power of your tongue; whatever you say out of your mouth today is what you're going to have for results tomorrow.

00:37:00.543 --> 00:38:23.856
